~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : inphr                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : inphr [<message>]

   This sets the message that is displayed following your name when 
   you enter a room. eg if your name is fred and you set it to 
   "enters fast" other people will see "Fred enters fast" when you 
   enter a room. If you omit the message it shows you your current 
   message.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : outphr, desc, set
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
